body:
@axelrb thanks a lot for your contribution!
contributions to the core repo require a signed contributors agreement http://owncloud.org/about/contributor-agreement/

alternatively you can add a comment here where you state that this contribution is mit licensed.

@deepdiver1975 
sure, the mit license is fine.
@houbaastef 
of course in many cases the webserver log is fine, but not for the standard form, so it would be good to have the alternative. i will have a look to make this configuration based.
i originally tried a modification in the user.php file which worked as well. but since this is for the form logins only it should be ok.
regarding the legal question i think on should always keep an appropriate log rotation in mind. by default lots of software eg, sshd logs the ip ...
